item.title: Contact
item.author: daniel.nielsen85@gmail.com
item.description: Send Great! We have got your details and someone will be in touch. $(document).ready(function(){ console.log(“test0”); $(‘#contact’).submit(function(event) { event.preventDefault(); console.log(“test”); console.log($(‘#message’).val()) $.ajax({ dataType: “json”, method: “POST”, url: “//formspree.io/daniel.nielsen85@gmail.com”, data: { message: $(‘#message’).val(), email: $(‘#email’).val(), _subject: “CrossProduct - Contact Form”, name: $(‘#name’).val() } }).done(function(data) { $(‘#contact’).remove(); $(‘.alert’).fadeIn(); }); event.preventDefault(); }); });
